published on 2021-03-13T20:34:21Z

Free PDF and Backing Tracks from the video in the link below. https://www.brianposton.net/lessons By request I transcribed another Jimmy Bryant & Speedy West tune "Boogie Man"! It's a fun to play riff based song, with 3 parts repeating over and over. Its a lot of fun to play, double stops and chicken picking throughout. Hope you can take something from it.
